\c 15
\s Mirairo yezvipiriso
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jehovha wakataura kuna Mozisi achiti:
\v 2 Taura kuvana vaIsraeri ugoti kwavari: Pamunosvika munyika yeugaro hwenyu, yandinopa kwamuri,
\v 3 muchiita chipo chemoto kuna Jehovha, chipo chinopiswa, kana chibairo chekuzadzisa mhiko, kana chipo chekuzvidira, kana pamitambo yenyu yakamiswa, kuita hwema hunonhuhwira kuna Jehovha, zvinobva pamombe kana pamakwai,
\v 4 zvino iye anopa chipo chake kuna Jehovha ngaauye nechipo chechidyiwa chechegumi cheefa yeupfu hwakakanyiwa nechechina chehini yemafuta.
\v 5 Nechechina chehini yewaini yechipo chechinwiwa uchazvigadzira nechipo chinopiswa kana chechibairo, chegwayana rimwe.
\v 6 Kana chegondobwe uchagadzira chipo chechidyiwa, zvegumi zviviri zveupfu hwakakanyiwa nechetatu chehini yemafuta.
\v 7 Nechechipo chechinwiwa uchapa chetatu chehini yewaini, zvive hwema hunonhuhwira kuna Jehovha.
\v 8 Zvino kana uchigadzira nzombe diki kuva chipo chinopiswa kana chibairo chekuzadzisa mhiko, kana zvipo zvekuyananisa kuna Jehovha,
\v 9 zvino achapa nenzombe diki chive chipo chechidyiwa chezvegumi zvitatu zveupfu hwakakanyiwa nehafu yehini yemafuta.
\v 10 Zvino iwe uchauisa hafu hehini yewaini yechipo chechinwiwa, chipo chemoto, chehwema hunonhuhwira kuna Jehovha.
\v 11 Zvichaitwa saizvozvo panzombe iyi, kana pagondobwe iri, kana pagwayana, kana pambudzana.
\v 12 Zvichienderana neuwandu hwauchagadzira, uchaita saizvozvo kune chimwe nechimwe zvichienderana neuwandu hwacho.
\v 13 Vese vanoberekerwa munyika vachaita zvinhu izvi nemutoo uyu, pakupa chipo chemoto chehwema hunonhuhwira kuna Jehovha.
\v 14 Zvino kana mweni ari mutorwa pakati penyu, kana ani nani pakati penyu kusvika kumazera enyu achida kupa chipo chemoto chehwema hunonhuhwira kuna Jehovha, sezvamunoita, achaita.
\v 15 Pachava nechimiso chimwe chenyu necheungano nechemweni ugere semutorwa, chimiso nekusingaperi pamazera enyu; sezvamuri mutorwa achava saizvozvo pamberi paJehovha.
\v 16 Murairo umwe netsika imwe zvichava zvenyu nezvemweni agere nemwi semutorwa.
\p
\v 17 Zvino Jehovha wakataura kuna Mozisi achiti:
\v 18 Taura kuvana vaIsraeri ugoti kwavari: Kana masvika kunyika yandinokuisai kwairi,
\v 19 zvino zvichava kuti kana muchidya zvekudya zvenyika iyi, muchapa chipo chinosimudzwa kuna Jehovha.
\v 20 Pazvekutanga zvemukanyiwa wenyu muchapa keke chive chipo chinosimudzwa; sechipo chinosimudzwa cheburiro, saizvozvo muchachisimudza.
\v 21 Pazvekutanga zvemukanyiwa wenyu ipai kuna Jehovha chipo chinosimudzwa pamazera enyu.
\p
\v 22 Zvino kana makakanganisa, mukasacherekedza mirairo iyi yese, Jehovha yaakataura kuna Mozisi,
\v 23 zvese Jehovha zvaakakurairai neruoko rwaMozisi, kubva pazuva Jehovha raakaraira uye zvichienda mberi pamazera enyu,
\v 24 zvino zvichava kana zvaitwa nekusaziva pasiri pameso eungano, kuti ungano yese ichapa nzombe imwe diki mhuru yemombe ive chipo chinopiswa, ive hwema hunonhuhwira kuna Jehovha, pamwe nechipo chacho chechidyiwa, uye nechipo chacho chechinwiwa, zvichienderana netsika, nembudzana imwe yembudzi ive chipo chezvivi.
\v 25 Zvino mupristi achaitira ungano yese yevana vaIsraeri chiyananiso, uye vachazvikanganwirwa; nokuti kusaziva, uye vachauya nechipo chavo, chipo chemoto kuna Jehovha, nechipo chavo chezvivi pamberi paJehovha, nekuda kwekusaziva kwavo.
\v 26 Zvino zvichakanganwirwa ungano yese yevana vaIsraeri, nemweni agere semutorwa pakati pavo, vanhu vese zvavari mukusaziva.
\p
\v 27 Zvino kana mweya umwe neumwe ukatadza nekusaziva, zvino achauya nesheche yembudzi yegore rimwe ive chipo chezvivi.
\v 28 Zvino mupristi achaitira mweya uyu wakatadza nekusaziva chiyananiso paakatadza nekusaziva pamberi paJehovha, kumuitira chiyananiso; uye achakanganwirwa.
\v 29 Muchava nemurairo umwe pamusoro peatadza nekusaziva, wakaberekerwa panyika pakati pevana vaIsraeri newemweni agere semutorwa pakati pavo.
\p
\v 30 Asi mweya unoita maune, wakaberekerwa panyika kana mweni, iyeye akatuka Jehovha; mweya uyo uchagurwa kubva pakati pevanhu vekwake.
\v 31 Nokuti wakazvidza shoko raJehovha, ndokuputsa murairo wake; mweya uyu uchagurwa kwazvo; kuipa kwake kuri pamusoro pake.
\s Munhu akadarika murairo wesabata anourawa
\p
\v 32 Zvino vana vaIsraeri vachiri murenje, vakawana munhu achiunganidza tsotso nezuva resabata.
\v 33 Zvino avo vakamuwana achiunganidza tsotso vakamuisa kuna Mozisi nakuna Aroni nekuungano yese.
\v 34 Zvino vakamuisa muchitokisi, nokuti kwakange kusina kurehwa kuti achaitwei.
\v 35 Jehovha ndokuti kuna Mozisi: Munhu uyu zvirokwazvo achaurawa; ungano yese ichamutaka nemabwe kunze kwemusasa.
\v 36 Zvino ungano yese yakamuisa kunze kwemusasa, ndokumutaka nemabwe, iye ndokufa, Jehovha sezvaakange araira Mozisi.
\s Chiratidzo chinofanira kuiswa panguvo dzavo
\p
\v 37 Zvino Jehovha wakataura kuna Mozisi achiti:
\v 38 Taura kuvana vaIsraeri, uvaudze kuti vazviitire chaka pamipendero yenguvo dzavo, pamazera avo, uye kuti vaise pachaka yemupendero rwonzi rweruvara rwedenga.
\v 39 Uye chichava kwamuri chaka kuti muitarire, mugorangarira mirairo yese yaJehovha, ndokuiita; kuti murege kutsvaka muchitevera moyo yenyu muchitevera meso enyu, kwamaisitevera paupombwe;
\v 40 kuti murangarire nekuita mirairo yangu yese, mugova vatsvene kuna Mwari wenyu.
\v 41 Ndini Jehovha Mwari wenyu, wakakubudisai munyika yeEgipita kuva Mwari wenyu; ndini Jehovha Mwari wenyu.
